Helped format documentation into a professional open-source standard.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Copilot CLI felt like an AI pair-programmer embedded directly into my shell. It reduced friction and allowed me to focus on system design and security logic rather than boilerplate.&lt;/p&gt;




